OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FOne in six people arrested across the
OL,7,Fcountry in connection with the unrest
OL,8,Ffollowing the Southport stabbings were
OL,9,Funder 18.
OL,11,FThe summer saw widespread rioting and
OL,12,Fdisorder following the killing of
OL,13,Fthree girls, Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,14,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,15,FStancombe, seven, at a dance class in
OL,16,FSouthport on 30 July.
OL,18,FPolice and courts were quick to arrest
OL,19,Fand charge many of those involved in
OL,20,Fthe unrest.
