OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FAn investigation by RADAR has collated
OL,7,Fthe number of arrests by police force,
OL,8,Falongside their ages and the offences
OL,9,Fcommitted.
OL,11,FIt found Greater Manchester Police
OL,12,Fmade the most arrests (160), followed
OL,13,Fby Merseyside (148) and the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police (142).
OL,16,FWhile the most children were arrested
OL,17,Fin Humberside (38), Merseyside (33)
OL,18,Fand Manchester (32).
