OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FResponses to freedom of information
OL,7,Frequests show there were 1,233 arrests
OL,8,Facross the 32 police forces that
OL,9,Fprovided data, 219 of them relating to
OL,10,Fchildren under 18.
OL,12,FThirteen police forces did not supply
OL,13,Ffigures.
OL,15,FAmong those to provide information on
OL,16,Fwhy people were arrested, public order
OL,17,Foffences were by far the most common
OL,18,Freason for arrest, with more than 700
OL,19,Fcases.
