OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FHowever, there were also 69 offences
OL,7,Fof assault, 45 of theft and burglary
OL,8,F(including four shoplifting offences),
OL,9,F38 for possession of weapons, 32 drug
OL,10,Foffences and 19 for malicious
OL,11,Fcommunications.
OL,13,FArrests can be for more than one
OL,14,Foffence.
OL,16,FThere were no arrests linked to the
OL,17,Fdisorder made by six police forces.
