OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FSeparate figures collated by the
OL,7,FNational Police Chiefs' Council found
OL,8,F1,711 arrests have been made since the
OL,9,Fend of July.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the organisation
OL,12,Fsaid arrests and charging decisions
OL,13,F"are likely to continue for some time".
OL,15,FThe spokesperson said: "Unfortunately,
OL,16,Fwe did see a number of young people
OL,17,Ftake part in these incidents."
