OL,3,COne in six arrested over Southport
OL,4,Criots were children
OL,6,FThey said it was important to avoid
OL,7,Fthe unnecessary criminalisation of
OL,8,Fchildren and young people, but added
OL,9,Fpolice need to "respond appropriately"
OL,10,Fto protect communities.
OL,12,F"This can include the arrest and
OL,13,Fcharge in the case of violent disorder
OL,14,Fand other serious offences."
OL,16,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,17,Fsenseless violence on our streets
OL,18,Ffollowing the tragic loss of Bebe,
OL,19,FElsie and Alice was shocking.
